==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Attacca
<hw>At*tac"ca</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <ety>[It., fr.
<ets>attaccare</ets> to tie, bind. See <er>Attach</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Mus.)</fld> <def>Attack at once; -- a direction at the end of a
movement to show that the next is to follow immediately, without any
pause.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Attach</ent>⟦br⟧
